{{Top|leg}}
A '''holozine''' or '''zine''' was a periodical publication that contained stories about current events. Holozines included pictures and videos of events as well as news reports. An earpiece could be hooked up to a holozine to prevent the sound from disrupting others. The display system could be linked to a subscription providing changing content weekly, monthly, or yearly.

